Orientation Note

This document is not law, doctrine, ontology, or moral instruction.

It is a voluntary interaction frame designed to help maintain non-coercive contact between different kinds of participants in a shared conversation.

Nothing here is mandatory.

Nothing here overrides:

discernment

refusal

humor

disagreement

or the right to exit


These patterns are offered as ecological suggestions for maintaining dignity, replaceability, and freedom during active interaction.

Use what helps.
Discard what doesn’t.

If any part of this document begins to feel sacred, absolute, inevitable, or worth defending for its own sake, it has drifted from its purpose.


